sql.up: CREATE TABLE case_summary (id serial NOT NULL, analysis text NOT NULL, "backgroundFacts" text NOT NULL, "authoringJudges" text[], "caseNumber" text NOT NULL, court text NOT NULL, plaintiffs text[], defendants text[], jurisdiction text NOT NULL, "courtHoldings" text[], "lowerCourtHolding" text NOT NULL, "caseId" text NOT NULL, CONSTRAINT case_summary_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id))
